Name: Zion Cannabis
Description: A little about us..Perfectly nestled in the southwest corner of downtown between Portland State University & OHSU, we're a one-stop-shop for all of your high-end cannabis needs. We …Learn more about Zion Cannabis, Opens a popupSpecialtiesA little about us..Perfectly nestled in the southwest corner of downtown between Portland State University & OHSU, we're a one-stop-shop for all of your high-end cannabis needs. We are open from 10am-10pm Monday-Saturday, offering a variety of high quality edibles, flower, & concentrates to the OMMP & Recreational communities. Visit us today!Our Mission:Rigorous pesticide screening and detailed terpene profiling means you get the safest and highest quality medical grade cannabis in Oregon.HistoryEstablished in 2015.Long before we broke ground on our downtown Portland dispensary, we spent considerable time toiling over what the ideal OMMP dispensary would look like. We knew from the outset that we would only carry the very best medical cannabis products available.But after many days of careful consideration, we discovered that we all share some other core values: (1) education; (2) safety; and (3) community.We value you being educated about how to find the best possible strain for your medical condition, so we've integrated terpene profiling into our menu system and hired the most brilliant budtenders in Portland to answer your questions.We value your safety, so we set a new standard for pesticide screening well above what the law requires.And we value your community. Because it's our community too, and unlike any other industry, the cannabis industry should be about coming together as a community, because it's been a long struggle to get where we are today.

Description: Jayne is a recreational dispensary like no other.Our dispensary was created on three simple principles, Great Atmosphere, Excellent Service and Quality Products - at the best …Learn more about Jayne PDX, Opens a popupSpecialtiesJayne is a recreational dispensary like no other.Our dispensary was created on three simple principles, Great Atmosphere, Excellent Service and Quality Products - at the best possible price.Your weed should go up in smoke, not your wallet.We've created a space that is inviting to all who visit.In fact, we wanted our moms to feel comfortable here... and they do.Think of us as your Cheers.Our bud tenders are super friendly and genuinely strive to make you feel at ease.They really know their stuff - which means you'll walk out with what you want, and not what you don't.Seeing is believing... come visit us today.HistoryEstablished in 2015.We never imagined the day would come where a person could walk into a store and buy a joint.Do you remember the taboo... the lengths it took to get your stash... awkward deals... never knowing what you were getting (oregano anyone?).It's come a long way and we could not be more excited to be a part of this industry.We started our journey with a few friends and family, a vision and gallons of coffee.What ensued was red tape, battles with regulators, construction delays and everything else that "could go wrong... did."But we couldn't be kept down, and Jayne opened in November 2015.Meet the Manager

We are passionate and knowledgeable and our carefully curated cannabis menu reflects this. We are proud to offer a refreshing and intimate atmosphere where customers feel comfortable asking questions about the marijuana products that may be right for them.To date, our team has visited over 90 facilities across Washington state to ensure that our partner's standards are as high as ours, and that our missions align. From those visits, we carefully select only the highest quality marijuana products and have consciously curated a cannabis menu that strives to meet the demand of the legal weed market in Southwest Washington, and Portland, OR. From the soil quality to the air, light, and water systems our partners utilize, we all work together to ensure that we are offering the most responsibly produced and processed cannabis products in the market that are manufactured to maintain consistency, sustainability, and growth as the marijuana market continues to evolve.HistoryEstablished in 2014.H.E.M.P. is the first cannabis business to be a member of several community and civic organizations including The Greater Vancouver Chamber of Commerce (GVCC), The Uptown Village Association, and the Vancouver Downtown Association, and were recently nominated at the GVCC's Business Leadership Awards as the "2015 Startup to Watch". In addition, we host a monthly cannabis culture event called "Sunday Sessions" where customers can enjoy live music and art while shopping and talking cannabis. Showcasing local Vancouver artists on the walls of our check in area, we provide a marijuana retail experience that is unmatched.
